@page "/"
@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager
<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<header>
    <div class="header-content">
        <div class="logo">Logo</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#">Link one</a>
            <a href="#">Link two</a>
            <a href="#">Link three</a>
            <a href="#">Link four</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="auth-buttons">
            <button class="login" @onclick="NavigateToLogin">Login</button>
            <button class="register" @onclick="NavigateToRegister">Register</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<main>
    <section class="hero">
        <h2> Bring Me Home</h2>
        <p>
            Adopting a pet isn't just about gaining a companion; it's about giving a deserving animal a second chance at a happy life.
            Countless animals in shelters and rescues are waiting for loving homes, often through no fault of their own.
            By choosing adoption, you're not only welcoming a grateful animal into your family, but you're also making a difference in the fight against pet overpopulation.
            Adopting often means you're saving a life and freeing up valuable resources at shelters, allowing them to help even more animals in need.
            Plus, adopted pets often come with the added bonus of already being spayed/neutered and vaccinated, saving you both time and money.
            Open your heart and home to an adopted pet, and you'll discover the immeasurable love and joy they bring.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
            <button class="adopt-now">Adopt Now</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pet-cards">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="Image/cat2.png" alt="Cat" width="300" height="300">
            <h3>Domestic Shorthair (Tabby)</h3>
            <p>
                Leo was found as a stray kitten and brought to the shelter.
                He's been in our care for several months and is now ready to find his forever home.
            </p>
            <a href="#">Read more</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="Image/Dog1.png" alt="Dog" width="300" height="300">
            <h3>Mixed Breed (likely Lab/Terrier mix)</h3>
            <p>Luna was surrendered to the shelter by her previous owners who were no longer able to care for her.</p>
            <a href="#">Read more</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="Image/Cat3.png" alt="Cat" width="300" height="300">
            <h3>Domestic Longhair (Calico)</h3>
            <p>Jasper was rescued from a local colony of feral cats. He's been socialized in a foster home and is now ready for his forever family.</p>
            <a href="#">Read more</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<footer>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Bring Me Home!. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</footer>

@code {
    private void NavigateToLogin()
    {
        NavigationManager.NavigateTo("login");
    }

    private void NavigateToRegister()
    {
        NavigationManager.NavigateTo("register");
    }
}
